						<div class="postbody">Are there USB to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serial_Peripheral_Interface_Bus" class="postlink">SPI-slave</a> adapters? The clocked-serial protocol for NES controllers and Game Boy Game Link looks a lot like SPI. Connect SCLK to clock, MOSI to strobe, MISO to D0, and /SS to a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multivibrator" class="postlink">one-shot multivibrator</a> from strobe.</div>

